==English==
====Etymology====
[[stereo-|ste(reo)]] + [[radian]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

#{{geometry}} In the [[International System of Units]], the [[derived unit]] of [[solid angle]]; the solid angle [[subtended]] at the [[centre]] of a [[sphere]] of [[radius]] ''r'' by a portion of the [[surface]] of the [[sphere]] that has [[area]] ''r''<sup>2</sup>.  Symbol: [[sr]]

